Society.Relationships:
Shadow dragons were a [[favored monster]] of the [[drow]] god [[Vhaeraun]], serving him and sometimes being sent by him to aid his followers.{{Cite web enhancement/Deity Do's and Don'ts|15}} The same was true for the [[Chult]]an [[demigod]] [[Eshowdow]].<ref>

Shadow dragons were related to three drow offshots. A special form of [[half-dragon|half-shadow dragon]], ''[[zekyl]]'', [[Shadow creature (template)|shadow]] [[Draconic creature (template)|draconic]] drow, ''[[zar'ithra]]'', and the ''draa'zekyl'' or [[drow-dragon]].{{Cite web enhancement/City of Wyrmshadows|2-4}}

[[Sorcerer]]s were sometimes known to form dragonpacts with them. The pact was called '''Elusive Disciple of Dusk''' and gave the sorcerer abilities to flee safely.
